description.en:
ChihuahuaSol ($CHIH) is Cute, Collectibles, and Unique Chihuahua's #NFTs Built on #Solana. Both NFT and the token holders will get an exclusive prize. In the future, $CHIH holder can buy CHIHUAHUA NFTs with $CHIH Token.

ChihuahuaSol ($CHIH) is already available in Solana Ecosystem (https://solana.com/ecosystem/ChihuahuaSol) and several NFTs marketplace such as Raydium NFTs Marketplace, Magic Eden NFTs Marketplace, and DigitalEyes
